sequenceDiagram
    participant Platform as "JUnit Platform launcher"
    participant StatsListener as "HikariStatsListener (TestExecutionListener)"
    participant Monitor as "ConnectionPoolMonitor"
    participant Lifecycle as "DatabaseTestLifecycle (BeforeAll/AfterAll)"
    participant DCM as "DatabaseConnectionManager"
    participant VerCond as "EnabledForVersionCondition"
    participant Test as "Test methods"
    participant MetricsExt as "GraphQLMetricsExtension (AfterAll)"
    participant JVM as "JVM shutdown hook"

    Platform ->> StatsListener: testPlanExecutionStarted()
    StatsListener ->> Monitor: start(interval=HIKARI_STATS_INTERVAL_SECONDS, default 30s)
    Note over Monitor: Daemon thread periodic health checks and leak alerts

    loop For each test class
        Platform ->> Lifecycle: beforeAll()
        Lifecycle ->> DCM: initialize() idempotent once per JVM
        Note over DCM: HikariConfig.createDataSource() and validate then register JVM shutdown hook

        loop For each test method
            Platform ->> VerCond: evaluateExecutionCondition()
            Note over VerCond: Compare currentVersion vs EnabledForVersion minimumVersion (SemVer)

            alt Version satisfied (enabled)
                Platform ->> Test: run test using clients and providers
            else Disabled
                Note over Platform: Test skipped
            end
        end

        Platform ->> MetricsExt: afterAll()
        MetricsExt ->> MetricsExt: formatClassSummary() then attach to Allure

        Platform ->> Lifecycle: afterAll()
        Note over Lifecycle: Log stats and check for connection leaks (pool NOT closed - shared)
    end

    Platform ->> StatsListener: testPlanExecutionFinished()
    StatsListener ->> Monitor: stop() (final summary)

    Note over JVM,DCM: On JVM exit shutdown hook gracefully closes the pool (10s timeout)
